name: SUPREME ARCH-MAGUS
summary:
Kt is an ordinary wizard in the Sky family wizard school, and his wife Thea also works as an elder in the same school. As Thea is moving out to the elder barracks, she kicks Kt out of the house and puts the house for sale.

“You are just a piece of waste who couldn’t earn a silver.” Thea’s last words still lingering in Kt’s soul. (It’s not like Kt is a lazy guy who escapes studies. Most of Kt’s meridians were locked down by a curse.) 

Suddly on the same day, Kt received a Rav from his maternal aunt. “Are you really my aunt?” Kt questioned with a doubtful gaze. “Yes, Kt… I have st 5000 gold and Heavly elixir to remove your meridian curse. Don’t mind asking me for more money. Your mom left a huge fortune for you.” 

From that momt Kt’s life changed as he brought a new flying pet equal to core disciples, new weapons, Villas, Fancy meals, and whatnot. Soon, his powers sore and he became a Supreme Arch Magus.
author: PeterPan
